<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Tribute Page</title>

    <!-- Internal CSS -->
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 10px;
        }

        /* Main Layout */
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        /* Image Styling */
        .image-box {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .image-box img {
            width: 250px;
            border: 5px solid #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        /* Content Section */
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .content p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Biography</a>
        <a href="#">Achievements</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Tribute to Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam</h1>
        <p>The Missile Man of India</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">

        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/A._P._J._Abdul_Kalam.jpg" alt="APJ Abdul Kalam">
        </div>

        <!-- Biography -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Biography</h2>
            <p>
                Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam was an Indian aerospace scientist and the 11th President of India.
                He played a key role in India's missile and nuclear weapons programs.
            </p>

            <h2>Achievements</h2>
            <p>
                He was awarded the Bharat Ratna, India's highest civilian honor. Known for his humility
                and dedication, he inspired millions of students across the nation.
            </p>

            <h2>Legacy</h2>
            <p>
                Dr. Kalam remains a symbol of knowledge, leadership, and innovation. His vision for
                a developed India continues to guide young minds.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>Created as a Tribute Page</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
